1- Install VirtualBox on Windows

2- Kubectl
Download to -> https://storage.googleapis.com/kubernetes-release/release/v1.9.0/bin/windows/amd64/kubectl.exe
Move "kubectl.exe" into "C:\Windows\System32"

3- Minikube"
Download to : https://github.com/kubernetes/minikube/releases --> Choose version minikube-windows-amd64
Rename "minikube-windows-amd64" into "minikube.exe"
Move minikube.exe into "C:\Windows\System32"

4- Open CMD :
> minikube version
> minikube start

--
Sources :
https://www.assistanz.com/installing-minikube-on-windows-10-home-edition-using-virtualbox/
